comments: It was interesting, i focused on sound/name, every word was XXXykow so it was simple to memorize, wopykow was the circle since it was the one with the "O" buvykow seemed like a chonky name which also matches the shape, zetykow, i linked it to the shape since the letter Z has 2 points and the shape was very pointy, it made sense, gafykow was almost like a cross, that's how i remenbered it and for some reason i feel like i'm missing one which i would go by exclusion, but i can't remenber for some reason
